lanetary orbital stability, we utilize the formulae of Holman &\nWiegert (1999) [AJ 117, 621], as also used by previous studies. In this work we\nfocus on binary systems in circular orbits. Future applications will also\nconsider binary systems in elliptical orbits and provide thorough comparisons\nto other methods and results given in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2013 20:03:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Oct 2013 20:10:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
